Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of 1,1-(hexane-1,6-diyl)-bis(pyridinium) dihexafluorophosphate in a solvent of (acetone + water) were determined at temperatures from (288.15 to 328.35) K by a synthetic method at atmospheric pressure of 0.1 MPa. The experimental data were well correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
